00:16:57.080 --> 00:16:59.660
We often use the
Schrodinger representation

00:16:59.660 --> 00:17:02.160
where the operators
are time independent.

00:17:02.160 --> 00:17:04.750
But in the Heisenberg
representation,

00:17:04.750 --> 00:17:08.310
the wave function, the state
vector, is time independent.

00:17:08.310 --> 00:17:13.050
And the time dependence of the
evolution of the quantum system

00:17:13.050 --> 00:17:16.240
