monochromatic electromagnetic

00:17:34.590 --> 00:17:37.820
field, the time evolution
is just e to the i omega t.

00:17:40.850 --> 00:17:49.600
So if you want to obtain
the Schrodinger operator,

00:17:49.600 --> 00:17:52.060
