01:23:35.660 --> 01:23:36.820
You project it.

01:23:36.820 --> 01:23:39.920
You get an electric field 0.

01:23:39.920 --> 01:23:43.170
It has an enormous
fuzziness, but it's 0.

01:23:43.170 --> 01:23:48.970
And this picture that everything
rotates with angular frequency

01:23:48.970 --> 01:23:51.620
omega also tells
